## Sockets (`sockets/handlers.ts`)

| Event | Notes |
|-------|-------|
| connection | Validates UUID from `socket.handshake.auth.playerId`; disconnects if invalid |
| `room:create` | Creates room, joins socket.io room, emits `room:state` to creator only |
| `room:join` | Joins room, `await socket.join()`, broadcasts updated `room:state` to all |
| `room:start` | Delegates to `RoomManager.startGame`; broadcasts `room:state` (STARTING) then after countdown `room:state` (IN_GAME) |
| `player:input` | Hot path — no try/catch; delegates to `RoomManager.queueInput` |
| `room:leave` | Leaves socket.io room + calls `RoomManager.leaveRoom` |
| `latency:ping` | Echoes `clientTime` + `serverTime` |
| disconnect | Same as `room:leave` for any active room |

Player upsert to MongoDB (`displayName` + `lastSeen`) happens on `room:create`
and `room:join` when display name is available.

