## Dev Workflow

```bash
# Start MongoDB
docker compose -f docker/docker-compose.dev.yml up -d

# Start everything
pnpm dev
```

Server falls back gracefully if MongoDB is unreachable (3 s timeout, logs error,
continues without DB — room/game state is fully in-memory).

